query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, substring(PerC.Snils, 1, 3) + '-' + substring(PerC.Snils, 4, 3) + '-' + substring(PerC.Snils, 7, 3) + ' ' + substring(PerC.Snils, 10, 2) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.Snils is not null
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '' OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.Snils is null
